            . On Thursday, the 14th of December, I was passing through <placeName id="t18201206-208-crimeloc1214">Greek-street, Soho</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18201206-208-crimeloc1214" type="placeName" value="Greek-street, Soho"></interp>
